{"version": 2, "width": 85, "height": 42, "timestamp": 1774079610, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/zsh", "TERM": "screen-256color"}}
[0.015854, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[J"]
[0.016524, "o", "\r\n  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\r\n  │                                                             │\r\n  │   nur — collective security intelligence                    │\r\n  │                                                             │\r\n  │   Three hospitals. Same ransomware. None of them know.      │\r\n  │   nur lets them figure it out — without revealing who       │\r\n  │   they are.                                                  │\r\n  │                                                             │\r\n  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\r\n\r\n"]
[6.023136, "o", "\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║  2:17 AM — Ohio Children's Hospital\r\n  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\n"]
[10.030988, "o", "\r\n"]
[10.031329, "o", "  LockBit ransomware. EHR encrypted. NICU monitors offline.\r\n"]
[10.031404, "o", "  The IR team has IOCs from the attack — malicious IPs,\r\n  command-and-control domains, file hashes.\r\n"]
[15.034939, "o", "\r\n"]
[15.035503, "o", "  But they don't know:\r\n"]
[15.035534, "o", "    - Is anyone else seeing this same campaign?\r\n"]
[15.035586, "o", "    - Does CrowdStrike catch T1490 (VSS deletion)?\r\n"]
[15.035603, "o", "    - What actually worked at other hospitals that got hit?\r\n"]
[20.044049, "o", "\r\n"]
[20.044595, "o", "  They can't ask. Sharing incident data could trigger\r\n"]
[20.04464, "o", "  mandatory reporting. Their lawyer won't sign off.\r\n  \r\n"]
[20.044671, "o", "  Unless... what they share isn't incident data at all.\r\n"]
[25.053501, "o", "\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║  Starting nur\r\n"]
[25.053592, "o", "  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\n"]
[31.069312, "o", "\r\n"]
[31.069651, "o", "  Server running. Now let's seed it with data from\r\n"]
[31.069687, "o", "  multiple hospitals — each contributing anonymously.\r\n"]
[34.078089, "o", "\r\n  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n"]
[37.081935, "o", "\r\n"]
[37.082407, "o", "  First, hospitals upload their vendor evaluations.\r\n"]
[37.082415, "o", "  Each one evaluated CrowdStrike, SentinelOne, etc.\r\n"]
[37.082425, "o", "  nur strips all free text, keeps only scores + categories.\r\n"]
