[61.56283, "o", "\r\n"]
[61.563286, "o", "  Three evaluations uploaded. Each hospital got a\r\n"]
[61.563325, "o", "  cryptographic receipt — proof their data was included.\r\n  The server committed each value, added it to a Merkle tree,\r\n"]
[61.563339, "o", "  updated running sums, and DISCARDED the individual values.\r\n"]
[61.563386, "o", "  It can never recover them.\r\n"]
[67.570449, "o", "\r\n"]
[67.571101, "o", "  Next, hospitals share attack technique observations.\r\n"]
